| Scenario          | With 'utf8'                   | Without (Default)          |
| ----------------- | ----------------------------- | -------------------------- |
| English text      | Works seamlessly wikipedia​   | Usually fine               |
| Non-Latin chars   | Correct display datatracks​   | Mojibake or errors reddit​ |
| Memory efficiency | 1-4 bytes per char wikipedia​ | Varies, often wasteful     |
